{"id":"pattern-bats-hermetic-mocks","type":"pattern","fact":"The bats suite runs hermetic - no Docker, no IONOS credentials. test_helper.bash copies the CLI into a per-test temp dir and prepends mock 'docker'/'pass' to PATH.","recommendation":"Any new test reaching a Docker or credential path must use mock_docker_running/mock_docker_stopped/mock_pass_empty from test/test_helper.bash; never call real Docker.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"agent","reference":"test harness, issue #7","date":"2026-05-18"}],"tags":["testing","bats","mocks","docker"],"affectedFiles":["test/*.bats","test/test_helper.bash"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-05-18T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-18T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
